name: Daisy Ridley [Embedding]
description:
Another old project from my archive. I'm aware there's already another Daisy Ridley Embedding by Balbrig, but I figured the results are different enough due to differences in dataset and training settings that it warrants an upload. If you haven't tried Balbrig's embedding yet, be sure to get it as well!

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. When rendering full body images I recommend using inpainting. It also works well to let the AI use known information from the model by prompting for [Daisy Ridley|Koh_DaisyRidley] or [Daisy Ridley:Koh_DaisyRidley:0.8]. This allows the AI more creativity and it will get more varied outputs, it's worth trying.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
